  "time_ut": 1658306130,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1   \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Senthil Thondaman congratulates the new president",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "EC President Senthil Thondaman has congratulated Ranil Wickramasinghe who has been elected as the 8th President of the country in the parliamentary poll.",
        "It is expected that the new President Ranil Wickremesinghe will act quickly to recover the country from the economic crisis.",
        "Also, during the two months Ranil Wickremesinghe assumed office as Prime Minister, various steps were taken to get foreign aid to fix the economic problem in the country.",
        "On the basis that it is the main party representing the hilly people, the EC took a decision after conducting a multi-faceted discussion until the last moment.",
        "The decision was made on the basis of who would bring the country out of the economic crisis and who would be an internationally friendly person.",
        "The decision is always taken in such a way as to find a solution to the interests of the people of EC. It is on that basis that we have supported Ranil Wickramasinghe. We will extend full cooperation to his plans to restore the country. EC wishes the new President a successful journey."
      ],
